      "review_summary": "The PR wraps MiniMax music SSE frame JSON parsing in a try/catch, adds malformed-frame regression coverage, and adds a standalone local proof script.\n\nPR surface: Source +5, Tests +164. Total +169 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. by source inspection: current main routes MiniMax event-stream music responses through a bare per-frame JSON.parse that can throw on malformed non-empty data frames. I did not execute a live malformed MiniMax stream in this read-only review.",
